snippet.title: Closed Beta Test preview, enjoy Liyue scenery with Amber!｜Genshin Impact
snippet.description:
Long time no see, Travelers!
Have you been exercising all this time in preparation of this new adventure? A good health is the first condition in order to participate in this challenge!
If you still got things to do, you'd better do it now, because you are going to set off with Amber right away!
Hey! Didn’t we agree to go to Liyue together? Don't tell me you already forgot about it!
You remember now? Great, now follow Amber and let's explore the beauty of Liyue!

↓ Follow us for more latest news ↓
